Package: zabb
Version: 0.3.0-1
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34), libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.24), libgstreamer1.0-0, libgstreamer-plugins-base1.0-0
Maintainer: VitexSoftware <info@vitexsoftware.cz>
Description: Flutter-based mobile client for Zabbix monitoring
 Zabb is a modern Flutter-based mobile client for Zabbix monitoring system,
 enabling users to monitor and manage Zabbix resources from their mobile devices.
 .
 Features include:
  - Real-time monitoring of Zabbix problems with auto-refresh
  - Advanced filtering by severity level and hostname
  - Smart notifications with per-severity audio alerts
  - Mobile-optimized UI with ultra-compact design
  - Persistent settings and sorting across sessions
  - New problem popup alerts for immediate attention
  - Configuration screen with comprehensive settings
Homepage: https://github.com/VitexSoftware/Zabb
